Crime News Releases, available at http://www.usdoj.gov/criminal/cybercrime/ccnews.html. 

14 FTC v. ERG Ventures, LLC, 3:06–CV–00578–LRH–VPC (D. Nev. Oct. 3, 2007), available at 
