bcp/edu/pubs/consumer/alerts/alt128.shtm;  Botnets  and  Hackers  and  Spam  (Oh,  My!)  (June 
2007),  available  at  http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/edu/pubs/consumer/alerts/alt132.shtm,  Spyware 
(July 2005), available at http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/conline/pubs/alerts/spywarealrt.shtm:, Detect, 
Protect, Dis-infect: Consumers Online Face Wide Choices in Security Products (Sept. 2004), avail-
able  at  http://www.ftc.gov/bcp/conline/pubs/alerts/idsalrt.shtm; 
see  generally  http:// 
